Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.api.types

Class ExternType.Limits

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.api.types.ExternType.Limits
Enclosing interface:
ExternType
public static final class ExternType.Limits extends Object
A set of limits, a minimum and (possibly) a maximum.

These should be considered unsigned.
